The idea behind the project üá∫üá∏ 
The project was conceptualized to address the challenges faced by individuals in an unstable economic climate where access to health and emergency services is hindered due to various reasons.

The application aims to provide seamless care to those who cannot afford to pay for consultations with healthcare professionals by utilizing cutting-edge artificial intelligence. This innovative solution offers the best possible support while clearly communicating the risks and referring users to nearby face-to-face services when necessary.

The AI-powered system can cater to a wide range of healthcare needs, from treating common colds to caring for patients with less severe symptoms. It can also direct users to the nearest medical facility or arrange a telemedicine consultation with a qualified professional.

The billing model is flexible, with AI care being completely free, while live telemedicine consultations are charged per hour or per consultation. The AI algorithms will calculate the most appropriate billing model, ensuring that users receive the best service at the lowest possible price.

To maintain transparency, all AI algorithms and billing per service will be open source and approved by the community. Although the project is not entirely philanthropic, the profitability of the telemedicine model will help support the free activities offered by the app.

